node.text:
Today, women can’t earn a living wage playing professional hockey. They are dedicated to a world-class athletic training regime while also working important full time jobs that impact our communities: teachers, firefighters, doctors.

We’re proud to work with the @pwhpa towards our shared mission of a sustainable and viable professional league, so female athletes can earn a living wage playing the sport we all love. #WomensMovementNeverStops

Learn more about what you can to do support the growth of girls’ and women’s hockey at the link in our bio, and watch professional women’s hockey live on @nhlonnbcsports in the US and @sportsnet in Canada at 3 PM ET Saturday, March 6th from the @unitedcenter!

The custom skates honoring Willie O’Ree would not have been possible without the efforts of Wayne Simmonds, @jtbrown23, Eustace King or Terry Smith. Watch as they discuss the inspiration behind the skates, and talk about what Willie means to them.

The game-worn skates will be auctioned off by the @NHL, with proceeds benefitting @BlackGirlHockeyClub. Learn more at the link in our bio. #BlackHistoryMonth #NHLBlackHistory
